====教学生涯====

1925年，勒梅特在美国取得博士学位后，回到鲁汶天主教大学当兼职講師，教授数学和物理。

二十世纪三十年代，他陆陆续续在美国几所大学充当客座教授：哈佛大学，麻省理工学院，[[加州理工學院|加州理工学院]]，美国天主教大学以及普林斯顿大学<ref name = "proceedings"/>。

据一位他四十年代数学系的学生回忆，勒梅特是“一个博学的智者，但不是一个好的教育家⋯⋯有点像向日葵教授（漫画《[[丁丁历险记|丁丁历险记]]》中的人物）。<ref name="student">{{cite news |author1=Christine Borowiak |title=Georges Lemaître : "Un grand savant, très accessible... un peu Tournesol aussi", se souvient une de ses étudiantes |url=https://www.rtbf.be/info/regions/detail_georges-lemaitre-souvenirs-d-unif-d-une-de-ses-etudiantes-thudiniennes?id=10525174 |accessdate=2020-10-31 |work=RTBF Info |date=2020-06-18 |language=fr |archive-date=2021-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211201181745/https://www.rtbf.be/info/regions/detail_georges-lemaitre-souvenirs-d-unif-d-une-de-ses-etudiantes-thudiniennes?id=10525174 }}</ref>”他从来不备课，来上课的第一句话常常是：上节课我们上到哪儿了？学生告诉他，他于是接下去讲他要讲的东西。上课的时候，他解释一个计算过程：从这里到那里用某某公式，很容易就算好了。这时学生会提醒他，这个某某公式他从来没教过..... 于是他就转去解释这个公式<ref name="student"/>。

有次期末口试，他问学生问题，学生回答说这些您从来没教过，于是他叫学生把课堂笔记给他看，他翻了一遍之后说好吧的确没教过，重新问了其它问题<ref name="student"/>。

当时学校已经有电子计算机了，于是他把学生分成两拨，一拨用计算机计算，另一拨人工计算，如果算出来的两个结果不一样，就把学生重新分组，继续计算。但是他会分给学生啤酒作为奖励<ref name="student"/>。

尽管在教学当中他常常有遗忘的小毛病，但是他为人可亲，平易近人，课上课后都经常与学生互动交流。

=====中國=====
勒梅特在1926年回鲁汶大学教书的时候，被任命为鲁汶中国天主教学生之家的负责人，負責他們的住宿及[[随行神职人员|宗教生活]]<ref>{{cite news |author1=Sean Salai, S.J. |title=The faith and science of Georges Lemaître, father of the Big Bang |url=https://www.americamagazine.org/faith/2016/05/25/faith-and-science-georges-lemaitre-father-big-bang |accessdate=2020-10-31 |work=America Magazine |date=2016-05-25 |language=en |archive-date=2021-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210602061222/https://www.americamagazine.org/faith/2016/05/25/faith-and-science-georges-lemaitre-father-big-bang }}</ref>，并且在1928-1958年间与毕业后的中国学生保持书信来往。這些書信仍保留在鲁汶大学的资料中心<ref>{{cite web |author1=Lemaître, Georges |title=Correspondance avec d'anciens étudiants chinois. |url=https://archives.uclouvain.be/atom/index.php/correspondance-avec-danciens-etudiants-chinois |website=Archives de l'Université catholique de Louvain |accessdate=2020-10-31 |archive-date=2021-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210602062835/https://archives.uclouvain.be/atom/index.php/correspondance-avec-danciens-etudiants-chinois }}</ref>。

===宗教与科学===

1920年，勒梅特进入[[梅赫伦|梅赫伦]]的修院学习神学，决定献身教会；1923年，他完成修行成为神父<ref>{{cite news |last1=O’Raifeartaigh |first1=Cormac |title=Georges Lemaître: the Belgian priest who preached the Big Bang |url=https://www.irishtimes.com/news/science/georges-lema%C3%AEtre-the-belgian-priest-who-preached-the-big-bang-1.2697978 |accessdate=2020-10-31 |work=The Irish Times |date=2016-06-30 |language=en |archive-date=2021-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211117230617/https://www.irishtimes.com/news/science/georges-lema%C3%AEtre-the-belgian-priest-who-preached-the-big-bang-1.2697978 }}</ref>。

他说：“于我而言，科学和宗教信仰，在探索追求真理的道路上，缺一不可。”<ref>{{cite news |author1=Pablo de Felipe |title=Georges Lemaître, the Scientist and Priest who "Could Conceive the Beginning of the Universe" - Articles |url=https://biologos.org/articles/georges-lemaitre-the-scientist-and-priest-who-could-conceive-the-beginning-of-the-universe |accessdate=2020-10-31 |work=BioLogos |date=2017-08-23 |archive-date=2022-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220323041925/https://biologos.org/articles/georges-lemaitre-the-scientist-and-priest-who-could-conceive-the-beginning-of-the-universe }}</ref>

1951年，教皇[[庇護十二世|庇护十二世]]宣称勒梅特的理论为天主教提供了科学上的依据<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://w2.vatican.va/content/pius-xii/it/speeches/1951/documents/hf_p-xii_spe_19511122_di-serena.html|title=Ai Cardinali, ai Legati delle Nazioni Estere e ai Soci della Pontificia Accademia delle Scienze|last=Pope XII|date=1951-11-22|website=www.vatican.va|access-date=2018-09-03|archive-date=2020-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200613003427/http://w2.vatican.va/content/pius-xii/it/speeches/1951/documents/hf_p-xii_spe_19511122_di-serena.html}}</ref>。勒梅特对教皇的言论表示不满，认为自己的理论是中立的，宗教与他的理论没有任何联系<ref>{{cite book|title=Seeking Ultimates: An Intuitive Guide to Physics, Second Edition|date=1999|publisher=CRC Press|isbn=978-0-7503-0657-7|author=Peter T. Landsberg|page=[https://archive.org/details/seekingultimates0000land/page/236 236]|quote=Indeed the attempt in 1951 by Pope Pius XII to look forward to a time when creation would be established by science was resented by several physicists, notably by George Gamow and even George Lemaitre, a member of the Pontifical Academy.|url=https://archive.org/details/seekingultimates0000land/page/236}}</ref>。勒梅特和教皇的科学顾问丹尼尔·奥·康奈尔说服教皇不要公开提及神创论，以及不要再发表关于宇宙学的看法<ref>{{cite book|title=Big Bang|date=2010|publisher=HarperCollins UK|isbn=978-0-00-737550-9 |author=Simon Singh|page=362|quote=Lemaître was determined to discourage the Pope from making proclamations about cosmology, partly to halt the embarrassment that was being caused to supporters of the Big Bang, but also to avoid any potential difficulties for the Church. ...Lemaître contacted Daniel O'Connell, director of the Vatican Observatory and the Pope's science advisor, and suggested that together they try to persuade the Pope to keep quiet on cosmology. The Pope was surprisingly compliant and agreed to the request–the Big Bang would no longer be a matter suitable for Papal addresses.}}</ref>。勒梅特認為宗教與科學並非互相沖突<ref>Crawley, William. 2012. "[https://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/legacy/ni/2012/06/father_of_the_big_bang.html Father of the Big Bang] {{Wayback|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/legacy/ni/2012/06/father_of_the_big_bang.html |date=20150501001255 }}". BBC.</ref>，但他亦反對將二者混為一談<ref>{{cite book|title=Big Bang|date=2010|publisher=HarperCollins UK|isbn=978-0-00-737550-9|author=Simon Singh|page=362}}</ref>。

1960年，勒梅特被教皇[[若望二十三世|约翰二十三世]]任命为[[宗座科學院|宗座科學院]]的主席<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.pas.va/content/accademia/en/academicians/deceased/lemaitre.html|title=Georges Lemaitre|website=Pontifical Academy of Science|access-date=2018-09-04|archive-date=2021-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211019054229/http://www.pas.va/content/accademia/en/academicians/deceased/lemaitre.html}}</ref>。

===逝世===

1964年，他心脏病发作一次，健康情况非常不好<ref>{{cite journal |last1=McCann |first1=Joseph |title=Georges Lemaître: the Priest Who Proposed the 'Big Bang' |journal=Studies: An Irish Quarterly Review |date=2016 |volume=105 |issue=418 |pages=212–224 |url=https://www.jstor.org/stable/24871665 |issn=0039-3495 |access-date=2020-10-30 |archive-date=2021-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210602061333/https://www.jstor.org/stable/24871665 }}</ref>。

1965年，他的助手兼同事奥登·奥达尔前来告诉他美国的两个科学家发现了宇宙微波背景辐射，进一步证明了他关于宇宙起源的猜想<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/science/georges-lemaitre-priest-universe-expanding-big-bang-hubble-space-cosmic-egg-astronomer-physics-a8449926.html|title=Georges Lemaître: Who was the Belgian priest who discovered the universe is expanding?|date=2018-07-16|accessdate=2020-10-29|archive-date=2018-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180717030156/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/science/georges-lemaitre-priest-universe-expanding-big-bang-hubble-space-cosmic-egg-astronomer-physics-a8449926.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1966年6月20日，已经患有白血病的勒梅特在挚友查尔斯·曼巴克的陪伴下于鲁汶的圣皮埃尔医院逝世<ref>{{cite journal |title=Georges Lemaitre (obituary) |journal=Quarterly Journal of the Royal Astronomical Society |volume=8 |page=294-297 |url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/full/1967QJRAS...8..294. |accessdate=2020-10-30 |archive-date=2021-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210602062743/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/full/1967QJRAS...8..294. }}</ref>。6月24日，在雨中，他的灵柩回到故乡沙勒罗瓦，葬在马西内尔的家族墓地中。

